songs.title: Meri Jeet
songs.lyrics:
[Hook (x4)]
Meri jeet...
Sabse zyada zaroori cheez

[Verse 1]
Dekho kivein, duniya wale duniya te jaal paan
Jehda jittda ohde hi gale ‘ch haar paan
Jehda haarda ohdi jaan ni lende jaan dende
Ohnu ve jehda jittda ohnu ni den jaan

Oh ajj qabar khode, kal na manne ve jehda
Zyada bole, gal na manne ve jehda
Media de jhoothe jaal nu puche sawaal
Jehda maut nu hal na manne

Par jo ladhe, oh aggay badhe
Ve jehda maut ton daray, ohi pehlan maray
Naale dass saal pehlan
Jinha mundeya ne mainu agge kita
Ajje vi ohi mere piche khade

Laike, kaali bandookan, maaran nu tyar
Mainu halla sheri dende mere naa’ de naale maar
Hoshiyar jiven bhukha sher labhe shikaar
Kehnde "Saadi jeet inni zaroori assi haaran nu tayaar"

[Hook (x4)]
Meri jeet...
Sabse zyada zaroori cheez

[Verse 2]
Meri awaaz! sun gym ‘ch kad de munde dole
Meri awaaz! sun soni kudiyan da dil dole
Meri awaaz! jiven court ‘ch judge da ae faisla
Saare gaur naal sunan jadon Raja bole

Meri awaaz! sun gym ‘ch kad de munde dole
Meri awaaz! sun soni kudiyan da dil dole
Meri awaaz! jadon puchhan maitho raaz main kehna
Meri awaaz ainni uchi baki lagan saare thalle

Naale ajje vi main jithe meri challe
Ajje vi track main produce karaa poore kalle
Yaani, ajje vi mainu kise di lod ni
Naale bank ‘ch hon mere note ainne palle

Hun main poore karaan shonk avalle
Sohni SMS di jagah te Snapchat kalle
Kehndi check kari kalle teri akhaan layi cheez
Sohni strip kare video ‘ch pichhe vajje mera geet

[Hook (x4)]
Meri jeet...
Sabse zyada zaroori cheez
